videos.headline: Potter rocks the rim with huge slam
videos.description: Wisconsin's Micah Potter gets the ball in the paint and goes up for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Potter rocks the rim with huge slam) 2020/12/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carlson delivers monster block
videos.description: Green Bay's Paris Taylor goes up for the basket, but Wisconsin freshman Ben Carlson meets him with a huge swat.

videos.headline: Wisconsin trounces Green Bay on both ends of the floor
videos.description: The No. 4 Badgers are fueled by Tyler Wahl's double-double as they cruise to an 82-42 win over Green Bay.
